  <brief_title>Pain Relief by Intra-Peritoneal Ropivacaine During Gynecological Laparoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pain Relief by Continuous Intra-Peritoneal Nebulization of Ropivacaine During Gynecological Laparoscopic Surgery</official_title>
