  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In our prospective, randomized, placebo controlled and double-blinded study we will study the
      efficacy of intraperitoneal ropivacaine nebulization on pain relief during gynecological
      laparoscopic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
